data.description: Say Hello to this beautiful single story ranch located in Espyville, PA. Located just a short distance from the Pymatuning Reservoir and the Espyville boat launch, activities such as boating and fishing are only a short distance away. This home features a large main bedroom, two additional bedrooms, a large laundry/utility room, Large eating/sunroom area and a large kitchen. Plenty of storage all throughout the home for many of your home life needs. Head out back into the backyard and discover the dual purpose shed. One side features a storage/work/hobby area with upper rafter storage, and the other a perfect place to store many of your gardening needs. Double wide driveway has the ability to park four vehicles. Grab your friends, and come and see what this home is Espyville is all about!!!
